#12619
alter~
the alter~
A fascinating alter has been constructed by someone and placed here.~
~
25 1073741825 0
0 0 0 0
1 0 0
E
'alter'~
This alter doesn't look like it was made, but moreso formed from some
foreign metal you've never seen before.  It's shape has no symmetry,
and almost no orderly formation.  The surface of the metal is very
smooth and rounded, no edges or corners, it shines in the light and
no smudges or fingerprints are anywhere to be found on it.
It consits of a number of thick columns of metal in an almost random
structure, but in the center of it some parts have cupped to create
a sort of dish extending out from the rest of it, and within the
bowl some kind of dark, ominous water has been pured into it.
~
E
water~
The dark water is pure and transparent, though almost completely
black.  It has no odor that you can detect, and doesn't seem harmful
as far as you can tell.
~
