#12700
???~
You're not quite sure what you've stepped into, but this is
no ordinary house.  The walls of this single-room building 
have been covered in large mirrors of many sizes, fit together
to completely cover the walls.  The floor is cold grey
concrete, but nearly completely smooth and without cracks.
A light radiates from some point of origin that you can't
find, but seems to be omni-directional as there is no shadow
to anything here...  The only other thing here other then you
is some sort of strange alter.
~
0 262152 0 100
D1
~
door~
262147 -1 12629
> act_prog p drinks from the alter.~
if ispc($n)
if rand(25)
mpat $n mpechoat $n _lbl As you drink from the water, a divine light surrounds you from somewhere.  You kneel to pray to the gods...
if rand(10)
if lck($n) > 16
mpat $n mpechoat $n _lbl ...And the gods answer your prayers and bless you with a gift!
mpoload 12620 1
mpat 12700 give gauntlet $n
else
mpat $n mpechoat $n _lbl ...And the gods have deemed you unworthy and put a curse on you!
mpoload 12621 1
mpat 12700 give goggles $n
mpat 12700 mpforce $n wear goggles
endif
else
mpat $n mpechoat $n _lbl ...And you recieve no answer.
endif
endif
endif
~
> act_prog p kneels down.~
mpechoat $n _lbl Your prayer is well meant, but something is missing...
~
> act_prog p weapon to the sky!~
if ispc($n)
mpat $n mpechoat $n _lbl XahXhaX blesses you for your warrior's spirit.
mpat $n c 'kindred strength' $n
mpat $n c 'trollish vigor' $n
endif
~
> act_prog p looks up at the heavens and cries~
mpat $n mpechoat $n _lbl XahXhaX tells you 'Why not?'
~
> act_prog p whines 'I want to be an immortal already.  I need more hitpoints..I...'~
mpat $n mpechoat $n _lbl The gods have cursed you for being an annoyance!
if mobinarea(12800) < 1
mpat 12629 mpmload 12800
endif
mpat 12629 mpforce plague mphate $n 12800
~
> act_prog p begs and grovels to the powers that be.~
mpechoat $n _lbl Your prayer is well meant, but something is missing...
~
|
S
